headline.main: Secret Life of Tweets Undoes Celebrated Voice of French Suburbs
headline.print_headline: Secret Twitter Life Undoes a Star of France’s Suburbs

lead_paragraph: Arnold Schwarzenegger informed NBC that he would not return to the TV show, which had struggled with low ratings and faced criticism from President Trump.
